snippet.title: Warp & Warp Longplay (Arcade Version)
snippet.description:
- Warp & Warp Longplay (Arcade Version) -

An unconventional (but fun) shooting game with a horrible tune, lol... Ps. The maze world looks like an early version of Bomberman.
For more videos like this, please subscribe to our channel.
